Sentencas: Yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) membranes were deposited onto porous NiO-YSZ anode supports by screen printing.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance test of solid oxide fuel cells with screen-printed yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes

Sentencas: Combined with La0.7Sr0.3MnO3-YSZ composite cathode, the prepared anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) were electrochemically tested.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance test of solid oxide fuel cells with screen-printed yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes

Sentencas: A typical SOFC with a 30-mu m-thick YSZ electrolyte membrane gave the maximum power densities (MPDs) of 0.26, 0.53, 0.78, and 1.03 W/cm(2) at 650, 700, 800, and 850 A degrees C, respectively, using hydrogen as fuel and stationary air as oxidant.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance test of solid oxide fuel cells with screen-printed yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes

Sentencas: Replacement of stationary air with pure oxygen flow exerted a significant positive effect on the MPDs of the cell.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance test of solid oxide fuel cells with screen-printed yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes

Sentencas: Using 100- and 200-ml/min oxygen as oxidants, the MPDs of the cell were enhanced 35.3% and 68.6%, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance test of solid oxide fuel cells with screen-printed yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes

Sentencas: Polarization analysis indicated that, at the MPD points, the electrode polarization resistances accounted for 80% of the cell total resistances.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance test of solid oxide fuel cells with screen-printed yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes
